---
title: Spiced Beef 'Taco' Naan with Fresh Tomato Salsa and Lime Crema
description: We're giving your typical taco night a little upgrade. Say goodbye to seasoning packets, tortillas and jarred salsa! Tonight's toasty naan are piled with Indian-spiced beef, crisp slaw and mozzarella. A little crema and fresh salsa provide the finishing touch to each 'taco'!
